.SH COMMANDS
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B delete\-user
deletes user record
.TP
.B delete\-user\-state
deletes any existing state information for user
.TP
.B delete\-user\-pincode
deletes pincode entry for user
.TP
.B delete\-user\-token
deletes the token issued to user
.TP
.B set\-user\-pincode
sets pincode for user
.TP
.B encrypt\-user\-token
